vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for an MF-1(A) Multifamily District on property zoned an R-7.5(A) Single Family District, at the southwest corner of North Jim Miller Road and Elam Road
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval
Recommendation of CPC:  Denial without prejudice
Z212-280(JM)
Note: This item was deferred by the City Council before opening the public hearing on May 10, 2023 and is scheduled for consideration on August 9, 2023.
